y of Cumberland, Maryland, 1965, Allegany County Historical Society, Cumberland, MD\n\n==External links==\n{{commonscat|Cumberland, Maryland}}\n{{Wiktionary|Cumberland}}\n* {{wikivoyage-inline|Cumberland (Maryland)|Cumberland, Maryland}}\n* {{Cite NSRW|wstitle=Cumberland, Md.|short=x}}\n* [http://www.ci.cumberland.md.us/ Cumberland, Maryland municipal government]\n* [http://www.downtowncumberland.com/ Downtown Cumberland, Maryland]\n* {{Gnis|590057|Cumberland US Geological Survey}}\n* {{dmoz|Regional/North_America/United_States/Maryland/Localities/C/Cumberland/}}\n* [https://archive.org/stream/historycumberla00lowdgoog/historycumberla00lowdgoog_djvu.txt History]\n\n{{Geographic Location 2\n | Center    = Cumberland\n | North     =  [[Ellerslie, Maryland|Ellerslie]]<br/>[[File:MD Route 35.svg|25px]] [[Maryland Route 35|MD 35 North]] \n | Northeast = [[Flintstone, Maryland|Flintstone]]<br/>[[File:I-68.svg|25px]] [[Interstate 68 in Maryland|I-68 East]]\n | East      = \n | ENE       = \n | Southeast = [[Oldtown, Maryland|Oldtown]]<br/>[[File:MD Route 51.svg|25px]] [[Maryland Route 51|MD 51 East]]\n | Southwest = [[Bel Air, Allegany County, Maryland|Bel Air]]<br/>[[File:US 220.svg|25px]] [[U.S. Route 220 in Maryland|U.S. Route 220 South]]\n | South     = [[Wiley Ford, West Virginia]]<br/>[[File:MD Route 61.svg|25px]] [[Maryland Route 61|MD 61 South]]\n | WSW       =\n | West      = [[Frostburg, Maryland|Frostburg]]<br/>[[File:I-68.svg|25px]] [[Interstate 68 in Maryland|I-68 West]]\n | WNW       =\n | Northwest =[[Mount Savage, Maryland|Mount Savage]]<br/>[[File:MD Route 36.svg|25px]] [[Maryland Route 36|MD 36 West]]\n}}\n\n{{Cumberland, Maryland}}\n{{Allegany County, Maryland}}\n{{Maryland}}\n{{County Seats of Maryland}}\n{{Law enforcement agencies in Maryland}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Cumberland, Maryland| ]]\n[[Category:Cities in Maryland]]\n[[Category:Cities in Allegany County, Maryland]]\n[[Category:National Road]]\n[[Category:County seats in Maryland